{"tid":2339504,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"Mr Organic 真係好HiHi","createTime":"2020-12-24T16:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T01:42:01.000Z","uid":323538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db4c00b5f948f14526d9ba976bb30ed9652f77ee","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"閪丫！有冇人識得呢間 Mr Organic ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrorganic.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrorganic.co%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=238ffca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrorganic.co/</a><br />\n<br />\n我見佢個牌面靚靚地，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌</span></strong></span>，原來黑店黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0668a6a5b4fcfe310f3715e6a380d600c0fba93e","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db4c00b5f948f14526d9ba976bb30ed9652f77ee","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"閪丫！有冇人識得呢間 Mr Organic ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrorganic.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrorganic.co%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=238ffca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrorganic.co/</a><br />\n<br />\n我見佢個牌面靚靚地，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌</span></strong></span>，原來黑店黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"【聖誕節都要和你追】 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBGsBao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBGsBao.jpg&h=1e7b415c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一上 @mrorganic 就見到「All I want the Christmas is with you and your pet」感覺好溫馨，實情老闆冷血到癲！<br />\n<br />\n勞工組事源於12月初已接到3位 MRORGANIC LIMITED 兼職員工求助，擔心老闆聖誕節走數。其中一位事主話10月中已經有部份同事神秘消失左，心中有不詳預感，所以早早到勞工組講聲。但去到12月7日糧期界線，都未入數。<br />\n<br />\n原來老闆好好，12月5號簽好左支票，但12月8日都未入數，仲要三位事主返荃灣拎票親自入銀行。最後銀行通知三位事主彈票，原來公司戶口無錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfBkbJO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfBkbJO.jpg&h=617cea9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但另一方面事主翻查招聘網站，仲發現公司喺12月9日請人，時薪有成40至50蚊！三個事主拖左總數成萬蚊，究竟老闆點解無錢出糧，但有錢請人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUKt43T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUKt43T.jpg&h=3610a177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今鑊真係聖誕節都要和你追，「all I want at Christmas is your payment and respect.（在聖誕節，我只想得到您的付款和尊重。）」<br />\n<br />\n我地都呼籲大家：<br />\n1. 唔好幫襯 無良 mrorganic 任何Whole sale了。<br />\n2. 一齊上 mrorganic FB 幫手追糧<br />\n3. 或者呼籲以下 合作伙伴 同 機構 唔好再合作了。<br />\n#香港拯救貓狗協會<br />\nDoggies &amp; Friends<br />\nPropet<br />\nCitysuper<br />\nThe Mills 南豐紗廠<br />\n誠品香港 eslite@HK<br />\nWild Wander HK"},{"pid":"71869cea724cd5e78854c3e23594086d475dd935","tid":2339504,"uid":203397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"空頭支票，報狗啦<br />\n善用資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b30d37b7274bf1ee63aad358bd014682f0a7f3","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db4c00b5f948f14526d9ba976bb30ed9652f77ee","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"閪丫！有冇人識得呢間 Mr Organic ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrorganic.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrorganic.co%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=238ffca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrorganic.co/</a><br />\n<br />\n我見佢個牌面靚靚地，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌</span></strong></span>，原來黑店黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n【聖誕節都要和你追2.0 】 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJPet1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJPet1e.jpg&h=61cbd67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「All I want at Christmas is your payment and respect.（在聖誕節，我只想得到您的付款和尊重。）」<br />\n<br />\n上回提及，MRORGANIC LIMITED 老闆拖左三位兼職事主人工，過左糧期都算，仲要銀行彈票，最後搞到平安夜都要和你追！<br />\n<br />\n24晚出Post 之後，靠著 24000 幾個接觸人數、2000幾個互動、同60幾個分享！老闆終於係尋日25號下午出返「部份」欠薪！所以話，團結好重要！除左三位事主付出之外，仲有「良心老闆」及「良心顧客」與打工仔同行！<br />\n<br />\n現時已有兩位事主出糧，但仲有一位事主差一個月，約2000元。老闆今次仲好有效率，下午聯絡，兩三小時之後就直接過數！（義工：Yo！出糧之嘛，洗乜拖？）<br />\n<br />\n但另一方面，出Post之後，勞工組再收到另外兩位前員工求助！表示於今年5月及6月任職。我地眉頭一皺，發現事情並不簡單！<br />\n<br />\n我地在此呼籲大家：<br />\n1. 密切留意事態發展，多Share 我地個Post！<br />\n2. 如果老闆「咁啱」留意到，希望可以出糧俾返五位事主，唔洗Boxing Day無糧過節！<br />\n3. 繼續做「良心老闆」同「良心顧客」支持打工仔！<br />\n<br />\n最後，祝大家聖誕快樂！<br />\n<br />\n香港拯救貓狗協會 HK Saving Cat And Dog Association<br />\ncity'super official page<br />\nThe Mills 南豐紗廠<br />\n誠品香港 eslite@HK<br />\nWild Wander HK<br />\nShopify<br />\nPetpathk<br />\nPaw Patch Club<br />\n爪子 &bull; The Claw Handmade<br />\nCookie &amp; Cream dog lovers gifts"},{"pid":"d3af4177664c9027e8045b6f12e15497d08da35c","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db4c00b5f948f14526d9ba976bb30ed9652f77ee","tid":2339504,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"閪丫！有冇人識得呢間 Mr Organic ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrorganic.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrorganic.co%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=238ffca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrorganic.co/</a><br />\n<br />\n我見佢個牌面靚靚地，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌</span></strong></span>，原來黑店黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:56:08.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"b58515bacfccb7566ba327e37b4e065ae41d20ed","tid":2339504,"uid":46838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"又開返Lu, 無事發生過一樣"}]}